description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from J-POP, ANIME, VTuber!

Includes the navigator and avatar of the popular hololive VTuber “Tsunomaki Watame” and the popular illustrator and VTuber “Shigure Ui”!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
 - Being low as dirt, taking what's important from me / TUYU *Locked
 - Overdose / natori
 - Chaos Ga Kiwamaru / UNISON SQUARE GARDEN
 - Chu, tayousei / ano
 - Idol Anime Edit / YOASOBI
 - SHUKUSEI!! RORI GAMI REKUIEMU☆ / Shigure Ui
 - Dreamy sheep / Tsunomaki Watame
 - I’m Your Treasure Box * You have found captain Marine in a treasure chest / Houshou Marine
 - Alibi Bunny / Usada Pekora
 - WWW / HIMEHINA

■Navigator
 - Tsunomaki Watame *with voice
 - Shigure Ui *with voice

■Avatar
 - UI(2D)
 - WATAME(2D)
 - UI(2D, casual)
 - WATAME(2D, dinosaur)
 - UI(2D, child)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Hit Song + VTuber Pack 5
